Package: sondage
Type: Package
Title: Survey Sampling Algorithms
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Ahmadou",
                  family = "Dicko",
	          email = "mail@ahmadoudicko.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Fast implementations of survey sampling algorithms for drawing
    samples from finite populations. Provides both equal probability methods
    (simple random sampling, systematic, Bernoulli) and unequal probability
    methods (Brewer, maximum entropy/conditional Poisson, systematic PPS).
    All functions return indices for easy subsetting. Based on algorithms from
    Tille (2006) "Sampling Algorithms" <doi:10.1007/0-387-34240-0>.
